#

Spicy Sriracha Guacamole

10 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackEasy

Description

A zesty and creamy guacamole with a spicy kick from Sriracha, perfect as a dip or spread!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • sriracha sauce: 1-2 tablespoons
  • red onion, diced: 1/4 cup
  • fresh cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
